# Cardzzz Visual Standards

## 1. Design Tokens (Source of Truth)
- **Primary Gradient**: `bg-gradient-to-b from-[#220020] to-[#560000]`
- **Cream Text**: `text-[#FFFADC]`
- **Accent Red**: `text-[#890305]` or `bg-[#890305]`
- **Chat Max-Width**: Always constrain chat area to `max-w-[650px]`.

## 2. Naming Conventions (Match Figma Layers)
- **Containers**: Prefix with `Layout_` (e.g., `Layout_chat`).
- **Major Blocks**: Prefix with `Section_` (e.g., `Section_navbar`, `Section_chat`).
- **Atoms/Components**: Prefix with `Comp_` (e.g., `Comp_logo`, `Comp_Button_Primary`).

## 3. Typography
- **Headings/Action Labels**: Use `font-roundo` (e.g., for the "send" button).
- **Body/Chat/Placeholders**: Use `font-satoshi`.

## 4. Glassmorphism (Cardzzz Variant)
- Use `bg-white/10` with `backdrop-blur-md` and `border border-white/20` for interactive layers.
